UNION SELECT 'Zōjō-ji', '増上寺', 1450, 110, 'Zōjō-ji is a Buddhist temple in the Shiba neighborhood of Minato. It is the Great Main Temple of the Chinzai sect of the Shingon school. The main image is of Amida Buddha. The founder of Zōjō-ji was Yūyo Shōsō.', 'zojo-ji.JPG', 'http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A2%97%E4%B8%8A%E5%AF%BA'
